summary: K so I’ve been thinking about the part in Infinity War where Spider-Man comes out of nowhere and saves Tony’s life and Tony’s...
body:
K so I’ve been thinking about the part in Infinity War where Spider-Man comes out of nowhere and saves Tony’s life and Tony’s like, “Where’d you come from?” And Peter says “The future!!” as he’s thrown away.

Ok. So. It was a funny joke, right? I don’t think it’s a joke. I think he really is from the future. I think he does his best to get there in time the first time, but doesn’t. Then he has to somehow go back in time to that moment to save Tony’s life. Like I think people save Tony’s life several times in that movie if I’m not mistaken?

And I know Peter’s wearing the old suit in that shot, but technically, the old suit is underneath the iron spider suit, so he just has to take it off…

The only question is how he comes back to life. 🤔

summary: The Avengers Saying Things I Overhear at my School— 7 :
body:
The Avengers Saying Things I Overhear at my School— 7 :

[Peter walking into the Penthouse after school two hours after he was supposed to arrive]

Peter, seeing one lonely slice of pizza inside a pizza box sitting in front of Tony: YOOOO ARE YOU GONNA EAT THAT MR STARK

Tony, holding the pizza an inch from his face: Uhhh, yeah. [Takes bite]

Peter, sad: oh come on, Mr Stark! I fell asleep on the train! I missed the stop!

Tony: well that’s what you get for sleeping on the train, kiddo.

summary: Can you even imagine being a Marvel fan as an IW VFX artist. Like. You’re a VFX artist. You love Marvel to death. Your company...
body:
Can you even imagine being a Marvel fan as an IW VFX artist. Like. You’re a VFX artist. You love Marvel to death. Your company gets hired to work on Infinity War. You’re so freaking excited. You get to create epic battles. Or cool space scenes. Or awesome suit-up scenes. Or anything, really, there’s so much potential here.

You’re handed your assignment.

“Kill Peter Parker.”

That person called it Spider-Deku, while I call mine Deku-Spider. In this au, the entire universe is differnt, with Spider-man villans crossed with MHA/BNH villans. The design is used with the average web shooter, along with the spider bot body. His quirk is crossed with spider and One for All. Soo yeah!
